excerpt: 'This paper reviews the current economic evidence on improving firm level productivity
in developing countries. Special emphasis is given to the current challenges facing workers 
and firms in developing countries, including climate-induced heat stress and natural disasters. 
Current evidence on the scale of impact and potential policy prescriptions are reviewed..'
date: 2024-07-01
